  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an action game of high-speed combat. It allows for close range combat and flexible switching of multiple weapons for combat. Different weapons can use different weapon skills, and flexibly using multiple weapons in combat will have different combat effects.<br><br>The game includes modes such as single player challenge, tower defense, player versus player battles, and player cooperative tower defense. In tower defense mode, players can build camps, recruit farmers, loggers, and miners to produce resources. You can recruit and command different types of warriors and set traps. Defend against enemies who constantly attack. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The character played by the player will shuttle through different worlds and challenge different types of experts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower Defense Mode<br>Players can recruit warriors to resist enemy attacks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561640/extras/dd63d8880ee126bd809644b5ca7790b9.poster.avif?t=1765154762\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561640/extras/dd63d8880ee126bd809644b5ca7790b9.webm?t=1765154762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561640/extras/dd63d8880ee126bd809644b5ca7790b9.mp4?t=1765154762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can also set traps to attack enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561640/extras/20b4684bf986ca3d1b67362c011a0477.poster.avif?t=1765154762\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"ht